---
layout: base.njk
title: "The Network — Electron Workshop"
description: "The Electron Network connects community groups, open innovators, and ecosystem enablers — and provides tools, services, and collaborative support to help them do more together."
permalink: "/network/"
---

<div class="mb-5">
  <p class="text-primary fw-bold text-uppercase mb-2" style="letter-spacing:.08em; font-size:.8rem;">Electron Network</p>
  <h1 class="display-6 fw-bold mb-3">Stronger Together</h1>
  <p class="lead text-secondary">The Electron Network connects community groups, open tech organisations, and ecosystem enablers — so they can share capacity, co-activate their audiences, and pick up heavier weights together. Network members also access a set of shared tools and collaborative services, available on a pro-bono or minimal-cost basis for community groups and non-profits.</p>
</div>

<style>
  .offering-logo { max-height: 36px; width: auto; }
  .provider-logo { max-height: 20px; width: auto; object-fit: contain; }
</style>

<h2 class="fs-4 fw-semibold mb-1 border-bottom border-2 border-primary d-inline-block">Offerings</h2>
<p class="text-secondary mb-1 mt-2">Offerings are tools and services that providers in the network make available to community groups — open-source, self-hosted, and built for community use.</p>
<p class="text-secondary mb-4">
  <strong>You don't need to be a network member to access these.</strong>
  Any community group or non-profit can engage directly with a provider.
  Network membership brings additional benefits — but the offerings themselves are open.
</p>

<div class="row g-4 mb-5">
  {% for item in offerings %}
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <div class="card h-100 border-primary border-opacity-25 shadow-sm border-primary-hover">
        <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
          <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2 mb-2">
            {% if item.logo %}
              <img src="{{ item.logo }}" alt="{{ item.title }} logo" class="offering-logo">
            {% else %}
              <i class="bi bi-box-seam fs-4 text-primary flex-shrink-0"></i>
            {% endif %}
            <h2 class="h5 mb-0">{{ item.title }}</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="flex-grow-1 text-secondary">{{ item.text }}</p>

          {% if item.providers and item.providers.length > 0 %}
            <div class="border-top pt-2 mt-2 mb-3">
              <p class="text-muted mb-2" style="font-size:.72rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.06em;">Provided by</p>
              <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3 align-items-center">
                {% for provider in item.providers %}
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-1">
                    {% if provider.logo %}
                      <img src="{{ provider.logo }}" alt="{{ provider.name }}" class="provider-logo">
                    {% else %}
                      <span class="small fw-semibold text-dark">{{ provider.name }}</span>
                    {% endif %}
                    <span class="text-muted" style="font-size:.68rem;">({{ provider.role }})</span>
                  </div>
                {% endfor %}
              </div>
            </div>
          {% endif %}

          <a href="/offering/{{ item.slug }}/" class="stretched-link btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm align-self-start" aria-label="{{ item.title }}">Learn more</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<div class="bg-body-tertiary border border-primary border-opacity-25 rounded p-4 text-center">
  <p class="lead mb-2 fw-semibold">Want to join the network or become a provider?</p>
  <p class="text-secondary mb-3">Reach out — we'll figure out the right fit together.</p>
  <a href="/connect/" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
</div>
